snippet.textDisplay:
Sorry if this is long
—
Hongjoong - higher tone rapper, he’s also the smallest of the group and he used to have a mullet

Seonghwa - if you’re offended by someone’s visuals its prob his

Yunho - the tallest member of the group. He looks like a really big teddy bear with a cheeky smile.

Yeosang - in my opinion he looks more foreign (japanese) than the other members. He holds the group’s last braincell and it shows bc he’s pretty quiet

San - his features look like a cat. Sharp eyes and high cheekbones. The camera loves him. He looks like Park Jeup from IMFACT

Mingi - deep voice and one of the taller members. He looks like BOBBY from ikon.

Wooyoung - he has very similar features to Jimin and if you hear a high pitched hyena laugh, it’s him.

Jongho - if you see someone just breaking fruit for no reason while singing that’s our maknae. He’s also the second shortest and he’s the one with the vocals.

This is how I tell them apart though but I hope it helps-😀
